OL,3,CDisremember: The award-winning film
OL,4,Cwith zero budget created by just one
OL,5,Cperson
OL,7,FA full-length feature film, created by
OL,8,Fone person, in 20 days, on zero budget
OL,9,Fhas won a string of awards.
OL,11,FDisremember is a psychological drama
OL,12,Ftold almost entirely from the
OL,13,Fperspective of a single, isolated man
OL,14,Fliving alone in a sparse London
OL,15,Fapartment.
OL,17,FLead character Rob is an ex-military
OL,18,Falcoholic whose unexplained blackouts
OL,19,Fand buried trauma drive the film's
OL,20,Fpsychological mystery.
