OL,3,CDisremember: The award-winning film
OL,4,Cwith zero budget created by just one
OL,5,Cperson
OL,7,FRob is played by Matthew Simpson who
OL,8,Falso took care of cameras, lighting,
OL,9,Fsound, props, continuity and direction.
OL,11,FMatthew told ITV News he took on the
OL,12,Fproject to "challenge himself" and to
OL,13,Fprove that without any support he was
OL,14,Fstill able to tell a story.
OL,16,FIt was filmed in Hackney to help the
OL,17,Fproduction feel "gritty and raw".
OL,18,FMatthew added: "Hackney has it in
OL,19,Fabundance. It has graffiti, rubbish
OL,20,Fand it feels lived in and real."
