OL,3,CDisremember: The award-winning film
OL,4,Cwith zero budget created by just one
OL,5,Cperson
OL,7,FDisremember took years to write but
OL,8,Fmuch quicker to film, a process that
OL,9,Fpushed Matthew's film-making skills to
OL,10,Fthe limit.
OL,12,F"When you're doing something on your
OL,13,Fown it was challenging to find moments
OL,14,Fwhen I was enjoying it because it was
OL,15,Frelentless," Matthew explained.
OL,17,F"There were a few moments when you'd
OL,18,Ffinish the schedule and do everything
OL,19,FI needed to do that day - just ticking
OL,20,Foff shots was the most satisfying
OL,21,Fthing," he added.
