OL,3,CDisremember: The award-winning film
OL,4,Cwith zero budget created by just one
OL,5,Cperson
OL,7,FDisremember puts the audience inside
OL,8,FRob's head to experience confusion,
OL,9,Frepetition, and paranoia exactly as he
OL,10,Fdoes.
OL,12,FThe film has won awards including Best
OL,13,FFeature, Best Narrative Feature, and
OL,14,FBest Actor at respected UK film
OL,15,Ffestivals with critics saying
OL,16,FDisremember never felt like a one-
OL,17,Fperson production.
OL,19,FIt took more than a year for Matthew
OL,20,Fto edit the film and complete the post
OL,21,Fproduction.
