OL,3,CDisremember: The award-winning film
OL,4,Cwith zero budget created by just one
OL,5,Cperson
OL,7,FMatthew added: "I didn't even think I
OL,8,Fwould finish the film, so to have this
OL,9,Ftype of recognition and to get it into
OL,10,Ffestivals is a huge achievement for me
OL,11,Fand something I'm really proud of".
OL,13,FA screening of Disremember and Q&A
OL,14,Fwith Matthew will take place at
OL,15,FRiverside Studios in Hammersmith on
OL,16,FTuesday January 27 at 6:15pm.
